SUMMARY:🚀 LinkedIn Post: Career Journey - GIS to Amazon HR
DESCRIPTION:Day 2 - Profile Boost Post\n\nCaption:\nFrom mapping geospatial data to mapping career paths — my journey has been anything but linear. 🗺️➡️👥\n\nI started as a GIS Engineer\, moved into project consulting in the energy sector\, then found my true calling in talent acquisition and workforce staffing.\n\nToday\, as a WFS Staffing Coordinator at Amazon\, I manage end-to-end hiring operations\, partner with NGOs and academic institutions\, and drive diversity in recruitment.\n\nWhat's the most unexpected career pivot you've made?\n\n#CareerJourney #HRProfessional #Amazon #TalentAcquisition #WorkforceStaffing #CareerPivot
