SUMMARY:💡 LinkedIn Post: 5 High-Volume Hiring Lessons
DESCRIPTION:Day 4 - Thought Leadership Post\n\nCaption:\n5 things I've learned managing high-volume hiring at Amazon 🏭👥\n\n1️⃣ Pipeline is everything — build it before you need it\n2️⃣ Agency partnerships need clear SLAs\, not just handshakes\n3️⃣ Data tells you where attrition starts — listen to it\n4️⃣ Candidate experience matters even at scale\n5️⃣ Compliance isn't a bottleneck — it's a safety net\n\nWhat would you add to this list?\n\n#HighVolumeHiring #StaffingOps #TalentAcquisition #HRTips #Recruitment #Amazon
