DESCRIPTION:Day 6 - Profile Boost Post\n\nCaption:\nDiversity isn't just a metric — it's a mindset. 🌍\n\nAt Amazon\, I've had the privilege of partnering with NGOs\, academic institutions\, and community organizations to bring diverse talent into our workforce.\n\nHere's what I've learned:\n→ Inclusive job descriptions attract wider talent pools\n→ Community partnerships open doors traditional sourcing can't\n→ Representation in the hiring process matters\n\n#DiversityAndInclusion #InclusiveHiring #Amazon #HRLeadership #WorkforceDiversity #BelongingAtWork
