SUMMARY:🚀 LinkedIn Post: Why HR Needs Data Skills
DESCRIPTION:Day 9 - Profile Boost Post\n\nCaption:\nHR is no longer just about people — it's about people + data. 📊👥\n\nHere's why I invested time in learning SQL and data analytics:\n→ Workforce planning needs real numbers\, not gut feelings\n→ Attrition analysis helps us act before it's too late\n→ Hiring funnel metrics reveal where we're losing great candidates\n→ Compliance reporting becomes faster and more accurate\n\nWhat data skill has made the biggest difference in your HR career?\n\n#HRAnalytics #DataDrivenHR #SQL #WorkforcePlanning #HRTech #FutureOfHR
