SUMMARY:💡 LinkedIn Post: What I Wish I Knew Before Entering HR
DESCRIPTION:Day 11 - Thought Leadership Post\n\nCaption:\n7 years in\, here's what I wish someone told me when I started in HR:\n\n1. HR is not just about hiring — it's about retention\, culture\, and strategy\n2. Data will be your best friend (learn Excel/SQL early)\n3. Stakeholder management is 50% of the job\n4. Compliance isn't boring — it protects people\n5. Every candidate interaction is a brand impression\n6. You'll need thick skin AND a soft heart\n7. The best HR people are lifelong learners\n\n#HRAdvice #CareerLessons #TalentAcquisition #HRCommunity #WorkforceStaffing #LessonsLearned
